locality: District Soalala, Commune Rurale Andranomavo, Fokontany Vilanandro. Tsingy Namoroka. Forêt d'Ambatofolaka.

NW: Mahajanga (Majunga) Province, Réserve Naturelle Integrale N.8, Tsingy de Namoroka, southern margin of main tsingy area, (Grotto with water Ambovonomby). Growing amongst slope of limestone boulders, very sharply eroded and with no soil, with open deciduous woodland
